──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
5. PROPRIETARY COMPONENTS
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The following components constitute proprietary intellectual property
of AMAImedia.com:

  • RandomScheduler algorithm (poster/scheduler.py)
      — randomised queue with configurable active-hours window,
        daily cap, and repost interval logic

  • AI Search Engine (bot/ai_search.py)
      — natural language → SearchFilter JSON pipeline,
        hard/soft filter separation, relevance scoring,
        and regex fallback parser

  • Commission Calculation Engine (core/models.py)
      — sealed constants: COMMISSION_RATE = 0.5,
        PLATFORM_PCT = 0.60, REALTOR_PCT = 0.40

  • Violation Escalation System (main.py, core/models.py)
      — configurable freeze/ban thresholds,
        rating decay, and auto-unfreeze logic

  • SheetRepo Layer (sheets/repository.py)
      — Google Sheets schema, in-memory deduplication caches,
        and retry contract for all API operations

  • Excel Report Generator (export/excel_exporter.py)
      — 3-sheet workbook structure, status colour coding,
        and in-memory generation (zero temp files)

  • 14-Step Listing FSM (bot/landlord_fsm.py)
      — state machine design, photo upload handling,
        and moderation notification flow

──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
6. SEALED CONSTANTS — NOTICE
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

The following business constants are sealed and form part of the
protected Work. Modification requires written consent from the Licensor:

  COMMISSION_RATE      = 0.50   (50% of monthly rent)
  PLATFORM_PCT         = 0.60   (platform share of commission)
  REALTOR_PCT          = 0.40   (realtor share of commission)
  FREEZE_ON_VIOLATION  = 2      (violations before realtor freeze)
  BAN_ON_VIOLATION     = 3      (violations before permanent ban)
  FREEZE_DAYS          = 7      (duration of realtor freeze in days)

